Package: simulateGP
Title: Functions for Simulating Genotype-Phenotype Relationships
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gibran", "Hemani", , "explodecomputer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0920-1055")),
    person("John", "Ferguson", , "john.ferguson@nuigalway.ie", role = "aut"),
    person("Rita", "Rasteiro", , "rita.rasteiro@bristol.ac.uk", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4217-3060"))
  )
Description: Functions for simulating SNP effects on phenotypes. Functions
    for simulating disease risk on probability and liability scales.
    Simulations to quickly obtain estimates of effect sizes for simulated
    genotype-phenotypes.
